commit.message:
Change major mode package to earthfile-mode (#8)

* Change major mode package to earthfile-mode

After discussed with MELPA team in melpa/melpa#7701. I
decided to change major mode name to earthfile-mode to keep it small scope of the
major mode that it operate only Earthfile only. If have any new tool coming to
the repository (such as LSP), we create new elisp file in the repository and publish
a new package to MELPA separately.

And including fix bug the major mode will enable when file name including word
`earthfile`.

* Update README.md

commit.message:
Initiate earthly-mode (#1)

* Initial commit

* Add basic features

* Support basic keyword highlighting base on https://docs.earthly.dev/docs/earthfile
  documentation.
* Highlight comment code.
* Toggle comment support.

* Add variable highlight support

* Rename earthly.el to earthly-mode.el

* Fix Earthfile not load earthly-mode automatically

* Use `[[:space::]]` instead of `\\s`

* Fix incorrect `WITH DOCKER` syntax

* Remove FOR IN out of keywords

`FOR IN` needs to implements on it own custom keywords because `IN`
can be match with variable.

* Fix keyword highlight incorrectly

Keywords should beginning at line start. And fix `"[[:space]]"` character
not work because it got escaped by `rx` function.

* Add FOR command back

The `IN` is not support at the moment.

* Format code

* Add header comment and lexical-binding

* Support FOR..IN

* Add ELSE and ELSE IF

* Update README.md

* Add code header

* Update README.md

* Update README.md

* Support SAVE ARTIFACT .. AS LOCAL ..

* Fix incorrect add extension

In example, it'll ignore `Earthfile` if we just put only `.earth` extension.

* Add screenshot

* Fix screenshot not load

* Update screenshot

* Add .gitignore

* Fix issues from suggested by package-lint.el

* Extract regexp in earthly-build-font-lock-keywords to defconst

* Make checkdoc pass

* Remove eval out of keywords

* Fix keyword highlight on target name

* Refactor auto-mode-alist

* Support .earth file extension

* Update doc comment

* Update README.md

Add contributor and remove highlight `.earth` file setup section.

* Remove .DS_Store from gitignore
